The **[rides to Denver International Airport](https://expresscoloradotransportation.com/denver-airport-transportation/)** that work best understand there are specific windows when airport processing flows most smoothly. Based on FAA [airport capacity data](https://www.faa.gov/airports/planning_capacity), DIA experiences predictable surge patterns where security wait times can triple within 30 minutes. The difference between arriving during a lull versus a surge can mean 45 extra minutes at security.

